The [[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] '''[[Booma/Legends|Booma]] Trooper''', also known as a "Grenade Trooper", were artillery units used by the [[Gungan Grand Army/Legends|Gungan Grand Army]]. The trooper used a miniature catapult to lob boomas into the desired attack area, similar to [[Gungan catapult/Legends|Gungan energy catapults]]. These units were very effective against shielded and mechanized units, however ineffective against buildings and non-mechs.

